{"tid":1907463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蝗蟲或大舉進攻 中國政府發出緊急通知 ","createTime":"2020-03-02T15:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T15:34:59.000Z","uid":227801,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60c3c3b91bec26f272c235f2b97b6495cd3f76c7","tid":1907463,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/Chinese-Urges-Preparation-For-Locust-Invasion20200302/5311269.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2FChinese-Urges-Preparation-For-Locust-Invasion20200302%2F5311269.html&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e7a833cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/Chinese-Urges-Preparation-For-Locust-Invasion20200302/5311269.html</a><br />\n在來自南亞的沙漠蝗蟲有可能大舉入侵中國之際，中國國家林業和草原局發出關於切實做好2020年沙漠蝗相關防控工作的緊急通知。<br />\n根據中國國家林草局網站在2月27日發布的緊急通知，2020年2月11日，聯合國糧食及農業組織（FAO）向全球發布了沙漠蝗災害預警。近日，沙漠蝗已從東非蔓延至印度和巴基斯坦，中國也面臨著沙漠蝗侵入的風險。<br />\n該通知說，&ldquo;專家認為，儘管沙漠蝗侵入我國境內成災的風險較低，但一旦侵入，將面臨發生規律未知、監測技術缺乏、防控困難等諸多不確定性。&rdquo;<br />\n通知指出，據FAO判斷，此次始於非洲的沙漠蝗災，因初期控制不力，可能會延續到2020年6月，屆時蝗群規模可能增長至當前的500倍。<br />\n專家研判，如果氣候條件適宜，此次發生的沙漠蝗存在從巴基斯坦和印度直接侵入西藏，或者經緬甸侵入雲南，或者經哈薩克斯坦侵入新疆的風險。"},{"pid":"3b4dbf623e22a7c746dc3fec26b1a54c7e6b7225","tid":1907463,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:25:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512008-20200302.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512008-20200302.htm&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=9f389bc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512008-20200302.htm&h=06dba043\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512008-20200302.htm</a><br />\n國家林業局發出通知，要求各省市做好蝗蟲防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n通知說，沙漠蝗蟲已從東非蔓延至印度和巴基斯坦，專家認為，儘管沙漠蝗蟲侵入中國成災的風險較低，但一旦侵入將面臨規律未知、監測技術缺乏、防控困難等問題。各部門決不能掉以輕心，嚴防因管理疏忽而發生蝗災。<br />\n<br />\n當局要求雲南、西藏、新疆等與印度、巴基斯坦、緬甸接壤的省區要高度關注、密切監測，在可能的飛行路徑佈置監測點，做好邊境監控工作。各省區要成立蝗災防控指揮機構及防控專家指導組，及時制定防控預案。<br />\n<br />\n各地又要加強監測工作，對可能發生蝗災的區域，逐一排查，適時發布預警資訊，及時引導輿論。"},{"pid":"07494785f51910a92d28f2e4fc2f84c15ee025ed","tid":1907463,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"支那蝗上蝗"},{"pid":"5d7f50c994c995f107349989401177d768e752ed","tid":1907463,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03c7ff22c486361edc3949af55499c814d914cc","tid":1907463,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:27:36.000Z","msg":"東張聽日即刻做個專輯話蝗蟲係肝炎聖藥"},{"pid":"5bfd5f2b6073e080e1efac51aaaf0bf79ea469e8","tid":1907463,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東張聽日即刻做個專輯話蝗蟲係<span style=\"color: red;\">肺</span>炎聖藥</blockquote>"},{"pid":"37c7188f4a20ed573a884c6e3ac77d5b4d7948d7","tid":1907463,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:28:06.000Z","msg":"多難興国，應該主動引入蝗蟲"},{"pid":"857aa948c9c445cb747e9ecfefb4703bca876113","tid":1907463,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"肺炎之後就係蝗災<br />\n十災"},{"pid":"b2e62b702b2201ed2dbbdbc7e674e270ba2f0223","tid":1907463,"uid":322822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:29:54.000Z","msg":"唔係已經被咖哩國全滅喇咩？"},{"pid":"51117cfec5d6973d60faa7b07b97f92da2f297f1","tid":1907463,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:30:15.000Z","msg":"唔係喺印度收咗皮咩"},{"pid":"97d7bf04f0d33decbac190121da6791eb65e0ed9","tid":1907463,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"今日hk01先話沙漠蝗虫唔適合係雲南生存 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijQBTeC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijQBTeC.jpg&h=6b7ae953&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}